Document for Moneyshare

This application makes money sharing easy 

there are times we have problems giving or taking money back after a trip with friends

its get tougher when lots of people involved and harder when some people give different amount of money. 

so this applicaion here can solve all those problems without any bugs maybe some ;)

program will ask number of people got involved, total amount spent, number of people spent money and then calculate with effeciant code and will give you the right result

test case

-----------------
Enter the details
-----------------
Number of persons got involved: 5
Enter the total amount spent100
Number of persons spent money: 2
1 )
investor name: james
invested amount: 40
2 )
investor name: thomas
invested amount: 60

investor name and amount:
1 )  james ,  40 .
2 )  thomas ,  60 .

-------------------------------
Amount distribution information
-------------------------------

Non Investor should return amount: 20.0
Investor james should get amount of 20.0 from other than investors with equal amount of 6.67
Investor thomas should get amount of 40.0 from other than investors with equal amount of 13.33

